Hoosiers have a choice to make.

We've invested billions in the Crossroads of America, and were still able to pass the largest tax cut in Indiana history.

This is not a choice between two candidates, or two parties - it's a choice between two futures.
The best days for the best state in the nation are yet to come. Let's go get it!
